      "writtenOn": "2017-11-08T16:16:31Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I was thinking of this as independent from the cleanup package, although I guess any handling of signals should be used for cleanup.  I have a slight preference for keeping it here, but could easily be convinced otherwise.",
      "parentUuid": "3f174091_c944b812",
      "revId": "327cf21ae30c426959c33492548c0e2da934a471",
